KeysToEntries.story_2_1_000:
Ryosuke’s coming
later, so just keep it
quiet, alright…
KeysToEntries.story_2_1_001:
What racer keeps
his mouth shut
before a battle‼
KeysToEntries.story_2_1_002:
I just went up against
that crazy 86
and I’m still pumped‼
KeysToEntries.story_2_1_003_2:
Don’t tell me…
you fought the
Akina 86 too‼
KeysToEntries.story_2_1_004:
What happened…
did you win or lose‼
KeysToEntries.story_2_1_005:
Beat me first,
then I’ll talk‼
